{"tid":372244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上環海味街咪又係水浸","createTime":"2017-08-24T08:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T08:15:03.000Z","uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0590fe091a9a5a891601afbcacb07d12e878cf9f","tid":372244,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:03:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20080608/11206702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20080608%2F11206702&d=x2ap%2B2O%2Fy76MWOXZsG3IF57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=0368e04e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20080608%2F11206702&h=22275612\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20080608/11206702</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20080608/large/08la4p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080608%2Flarge%2F08la4p1.jpg&h=5ebd7f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有水浸黑點之稱的上環永樂街，昨在黑色暴雨下受到歷來最嚴重的蹂躪，高達四呎的洪水湧入各店舖，令九成參茸海味舖遭殃，大批名貴貨品被浸濕，有店舖損失達數百萬元。受大雨影響之洪水半天後才退卻，部份店主點算損失時，拿浸濕的名貴鮑魚、燕窩，嗟嘆「一眶眼淚」。　記者：簡明恩、卓永強<br />\n<br />\n有「海味街」之稱的永樂街約有一百間參茸海味店，昨日受水浸的威脅比往年更嚴重。昨日水浸由清晨開始，至下午1時退卻，馬路滿目瘡痍，遺下垃圾、石油氣罐及死老鼠等，店舖更是損失慘重，店主及職員善後時長嗟短嘆，怨聲四起。"},{"pid":"40b7ce8341f8b3ca6bfdfd5939f58e3e64a1611e","tid":372244,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:04:18.000Z","msg":"08年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1cb2aec6ab416d0c7ca941b8b71d8e0e517fd1","tid":372244,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:05:30.000Z","msg":"1908年個次仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3573d5f68cf3ca67cd974587187620ed8bc9c943","tid":372244,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0cafb2834739f7dbc8e19b19d1a14b3a6df6d4","tid":372244,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:15:03.000Z","msg":"樓主坐左幾耐？"}]}